text: Five Golden Dragons is a 1967 British West German Liechtenstein action adventure movie directed by Jeremy Summers and starring Bob Cummings in his final movie role, Margaret Lee, Rupert Davies. It was distributed by Anglo- Amalgamated and Constantin Film. == Other websites == * * Category:1967 action movies Category:1967 adventure movies Category:British action movies Category:British adventure movies Category:German action movies Category:German adventure movies Category:Liechtenstein movies
